<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="rely-vi">rely <strong><em>vi</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /rɪ'laɪ/    美 /rɪ'laɪ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="rely-on-upon">rely on / upon</h3>
<p>1.★ <strong>依靠</strong><br />
to depend on sb / sth：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>You shouldn’t always <strong>rely</strong> just <strong>on</strong> the Internet <strong>for</strong> your research.
你不能总是依靠网络进行研究。</p><footer>2015 湖南</footer></div>

<ul>
<li>rely on / upon … to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>These days, we rely heavily on computers to organize our work.
现在，我们在很大程度上依赖电脑来安排工作。</p></div>

<p>2.★ <strong>信任</strong><br />
to trust or have faith in sb / sth：</p>
<ul>
<li>rely on / upon … to do sth:</li>
</ul>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I can rely on David to keep my secret.
我信任大卫，他一定会为我保密。</p></div></div>